To Build : 
	docker build . -t IMAGE_NAME
To Run :
	docker run --privileged -it -v HOST_REPO_CLONE:MOUNTED_REPO_CLONE IMAGE_NAME

1. You need to use --privileged flag to enable gdb debugging.
2. Before you build docker image, download cudatoolkit_4.0.17_linux_64_ubuntu10.10.run file in the docker directory.
